short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension will save your Google Snake highscore.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension will make your miseries end, this will finally store that highscore you made on snake.

We will in the near future update the extension to also allow users to share scores to a global scoreboard and possibly store the scores of other Google games.
